The Tsuruoka Police Station (Chief Keizo Sato) has launched the ``Bye-Bye Accident Zero Strategy&#39;&#39; in an effort to eliminate the high percentage of accidents involving bicycles and motorcycles that occur within its jurisdiction in recent years.
